{
  "texts": [
    "If Facebook can give me a categorical representation of the probable explanation, I would be really happy.",
    "Overall, categorical information representation is a fundamental tool for structuring, understanding, and utilizing data and knowledge effectively in various domains and improving cognitive processes, communication, and decision-making.",
    "Therefore, the explanation interface should provide users with more options for information accessibility.",
    "Explanation of a specific decision rather than explaining everything Participant responses showed that users require explanations of specific decision-making rather than global explanations.",
    "A global explanation is not feasible in this case because the users do not want to be overwhelmed with a lot of information that does not make sense."
  ]
}